{"tid":1403744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗日報William Luk俾黑警一棍打到暈喺地下","createTime":"2019-08-03T21:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:55:58.000Z","uid":34572,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"76a138ecdce03306c25a341f1157409c05ff53e3","tid":1403744,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:45:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/maddog.hk/videos/400379017268727/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmaddog.hk%2Fvideos%2F400379017268727%2F&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=e5ad545d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/maddog.hk/videos/400379017268727/</a><br />\n21:17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1924f027ae973f0a01278a66e7cfa9cc1ae93540","tid":1403744,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:45:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港九新界，遍地開花，<span style=\"color: red;\">八月十號</span>，光復荃灣</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n荃灣啲廢老唔食下煙唔識醒，狗總隔離集醫院，民居，學校，地鐵站，商場於一身，再加上地理位置四通八達。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日港島區奮戰，新界都唔可以衰俾人睇</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一站，光復荃灣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fa1a6928c8a05dbb3b80e6855417b0979ec516e4","tid":1403744,"uid":34572,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:46:42.000Z","msg":"城市廣播 City Broadcasting Channel (CBC)<br />\n1 hr &middot; <br />\n【黃大仙現場即時】<br />\n<br />\n約於8月3日 23：00 左右，癲狗日報記者遭受警方棍毆右邊面，導致該名記者疑頸椎受傷，出現暈眩及作嘔的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n期間該名記者即使暈眩仍堅持堅守崗位，繼續完成攝錄工作，其後短暫清醒過後，於 8月4日 03：40 期間再次暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67543314_3118315808195612_597528145851894